Revision history for Perl extension Module::PortablePath.

0.16 packaging & build updates
0.10 trivial documentation update
0.09 perlcritic fixes, changed to standard Makefile build process.
0.08 Moved to Build.PL
0.05 kwalitee improvements
0.04 cleaned up for perlcritic
0.03 support for changing LD_LIBRARY_PATH via the [ldlibs] config section

0.02 very minor mods to make it pass tests without /etc/perlconfig.ini
     also added an example eg/siteexample.pm demonstrating one way to override the default paths
     for example for those who don't have access to /etc

0.01 initial version based on internal SangerPaths.pm
